column2: SELECT  a.objID, a.l, a.b, s.waveMin, s.waveMax, f.profMean, a.airmass_r into mydb.MyTable from PhotoObjAll as a       JOIN PhotoProfile as f ON a.objID=f.objID   JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON a.objID=s.bestObjID WHERE a.b > #   AND a.b < #   AND a.l > #    AND a.l < #   AND f.profMean < #   AND f.bin=#
